    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Stands placed on altars or attached to the wall behind an altar, consisting of or featuring a raised platform on which a monstrance is displayed for the adoration of the faithful in the Roman Catholic Church.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
